<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="here/main_template/macros/master"
      xml:lang="en"
      i18n:domain="udala.zinema"
>
  <head></head>
  <body>

    <metal:desc fill-slot="content-description"
                tal:condition="view/editing_permission"
    >
      <p class="documentDescription"
         i18n:translate=""
      >
        Erabili elementu hau pelikulekin hitzordu bat sortzeko. Aukeratu nahi dituzun pelikulak
        eta sistemak automatikoki pelikula guzti horien informazioa biltzen duen hitzordu bat
        sortuko du. Hitzorduaren hasiera aukeratutako pelikuletako lehen saioaren eguna izango da
        eta bukaera azken saioaren eguna.
        Hitzordua euskaraz eta gaztelaniaz sortuko da baina pribatuan, zuk gainbegiratu, nahi duzuna
        aldatu eta ondoren argitaratzeko.
      </p>
    </metal:desc>

    <metal:content-core fill-slot="content-core">

      <tal:content condition="not:view/editing_permission">

        <tal:warning condition="context/show_warning|nothing">
          <p tal:content="structure context/warning/output"></p>
        </tal:warning>
        <tal:notwarning condition="not:context/show_warning|nothing">
          <tal:current condition="view/films_are_from_current_week">
            <div tal:replace="structure context/text/output"></div>
          </tal:current>
          <tal:not-current condition="not: view/films_are_from_current_week">
            <p i18n:translate="">Datorren asteburuko pelikulak ez daude oraindik eskuragarri</p>
          </tal:not-current>
        </tal:notwarning>




      </tal:content>


      <tal:form condition="view/editing_permission">
        <form action=""
              method="post"
              tal:attributes="
                action string:${context/absolute_url}/create_pelikula_events;
              "
        >
          <span tal:replace="structure context/@@authenticator/authenticator"></span>
          <table class="listing">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>#</th>
                <th i18n:translate="">Izenburua</th>
                <th i18n:translate="">Emankizun egunak</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr tal:repeat="pelikula view/get_latest_films">
                <td>
                  <input name="ids:list"
                         type="checkbox"
                         tal:attributes="
                           value pelikula/id;
                         "
                  />
                </td>
                <td>
                  <a href=""
                     tal:content="pelikula/Title"
                     tal:attributes="
                       href pelikula/absolute_url;
                       id string:pelikula-link-${repeat/pelikula/index};
                     "
                  >
                    Izena
                  </a>
                  <script type="text/javascript"
                          tal:content="string:
                                      jq(document).ready(function(){
                                         jq('#pelikula-link-${repeat/pelikula/index}').prepOverlay({
                                                  subtype: 'ajax',
                                                  filter: '#content-core',
                                                  })
                                                                       });"
                  >
                    Script
                  </script>
                </td>
                <td tal:define="
                      egunak pelikula/saioak;
                    ">
                  <tal:saio repeat="saioa egunak">
                    <span tal:replace="saioa/eguna"></span>
                  </tal:saio>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <button class="btn btn-primary"
                  type="submit"
                  i18n:translate=""
          >Sortu agendako hitzorduak</button>
        </form>
      </tal:form>
    </metal:content-core>
  </body>
</html>
